es/refresh.png\" style=\"height: 15px;\" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <span style=\"margin: 10px 0 0 -130px;\">\r\n                            <img class=\"callout\" src=\"/app_themes/dmca/images/callout_black.gif\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n                            You must be logged in and a Protection Pro member to do manual rescans. Click to <a href=\"../Users/Login.aspx?Redirect=%7e%2fProtection%2fStatus.aspx%3fID%3d3d24067a-89af-4267-93ae-9de6d8131852\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">login</a>.\r\n                            For more info visit the <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/solutions/view.aspx?ID=90382ba5-d2a2-4646-bb17-18365ea003c7&r=rectt\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">FAQ</a>.\r\n                        </span>\r\n                    </span>\r\n                </span>\r\n                <div style=\"\">\r\n                    <span id=\"spnStarted\">Protection Started:</span> <span id=\"ctl00_cntBody_lblStarted\">Unavailable</span><br />\r\n                    <span id=\"spnLastChecked\">Last Checked:</span> <span id=\"ctl00_cntBody_lblLastChecked\">Unavailable</span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div style=\"margin-top:10px\">\r\n                    <div id=\"divSpinnerContainer\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 5px; text-align: center;\">\r\n                        Checking Protection Status...\r\n                        <div id=\"divSpinner\" style=\"margin: -10px 0 0 5px;\"></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"timelineTooltip\" class=\"protectionTimelineTooltip\">\r\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\"></span>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"divTimeline\" class=\"protectionTimeline\" style=\"display:none;\"></div>\r\n                    <span class=\"timeline-lock\" style=\"display:none;\"><img src=\"../App_Themes/DMCA/images/dmca_lock.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"badge-legal\" style='direction: ltr;\r\n\t\ttext-align: left;'>\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n        <p id=\"ctl00_cntBody_pUnavailableBlurb\" style=\"margin-top:50px;\">\r\n            <!--<span class=\"help certificate-tooltip\">\r\n                <img src=\"../App_Themes/DMCA/images/help-circled.png\" alt=\"What's this?\" style=\"margin:6px -1px 0 0;\" />\r\n                <span>\r\n                    <img class=\"callout\" src=\"/app_themes/dmca/images/callout_black.gif\" alt=\"\" />\r\n                    This text can be customized.\r\n                </span>\r\n            </span>-->\r\n            <strong>Protection:</strong>\r\n            Protection Unavailable: DMCA.com has not yet scanned or approved this page for protection.\r\n        </p>\r\n        \r\n\t\t<p id=\"ctl00_cntBody_pLegalBlurb\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0;\">\r\n\t\t\t<strong>\r\n\t\t\t\tDigital Millennium Copyright Act:</strong>\r\n\t\t\tPart of the US Copyright Law. The DMCA addresses penalties for copyright infringement on the Internet and protects content creators by \"establishing procedures for proper notification\" to OSPs when copyright infringement is identified online. Online Copyright Infringement Liability Limitation Act, Title II of the DMCA \"adds a new section 512 to the Copyright Act to create four new limitations on liability for copyright infringement by online service providers.\" These procedures allow content creators or their designated agent to file proper DMCA Takedown notice to the OSP in case infringed material has been detected on their servers.\r\n\t\t</p>\r\n\t</div>\r\n      \r\n    <div class=\"cert-signature\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n        \r\n        <div class=\"magnify\">\r\n            <div class=\"mag-glass\">\r\n                <div class=\"signature sig-large\"></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        <div class=\"signature sig-small\"></div>    \r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n   